[V:5] z/ G, A,3 G, F, E, C,2 |
% T2: z/+E,+F,3+E,+D,+C,+A,,2=9.5 ✓
[V:6] z/ E, F,3 E, D, C, A,,2 |
% Bar: z/+C,+D,3+C,+B,,+A,,+F,,2=9.5 ✓
[V:7] z/ C, D,3 C, B,, A,, F,,2 |
% B1 original: z/+C,+G,,3+A,,+C,+G,,+C,2=9.5 ✓
